title: Page from "Libro de' Disegni"
displaydate: Sheets probably 1480-1504; mounting & framework by Vasari after 1524.
medium: album page with ten drawings on recto and verso in various media with decoration in pen and brown ink, brown and gray wash, on light buff paper
attribution: Giorgio Vasari with drawings by Filippino Lippi, Botticelli, and Raffaellino del Garbo
